CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, September 19, 1959, pg. A17, reads: "The Di's Fete Husbands - The well-known charity club, the DI's, entertained their husbands Sunday with an al fresco picnic in garden of member Margaret Watson. Between snacks, the girls discussed their coming March of Dimes production.  Seated: President Gay DeHall, Ruby Buchanan and Juanita Drake.  Standing: Gloria Grate, Elaine Jones and Margaret Watson. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of D. I. Club members, from left, seated: Gay DeHall, Ruby Buchanan, and Juanita Drake; standing: Gloria Golden Grate, Elaine Jones, and Margaret Watson, posed around lawn chairs at home of Margaret Watson
